detailed_results.request: Add a dark mode toggle to the blog theme
detailed_results.user_story: As a blog user, I need a dark mode toggle on the blog theme, so that I can have a more comfortable reading experience in low-light environments and reduce eye strain.

detailed_results.request: Implement automated chart quality validation to catch zone boundary violations before publication
detailed_results.user_story: As a Quality Engineer, I need an automated system for chart quality validation to catch zone boundary violations, so that chart publications maintain accuracy and compliance with zone definitions.

detailed_results.request: Create a real-time collaboration system where multiple writers can edit articles simultaneously with conflict resolution
detailed_results.user_story: As a writer, I need a real-time collaboration system for editing articles simultaneously with conflict resolution, so that we can enhance productivity and ensure article quality without disruptions.
As a blog reader, I need an enhanced blog experience, so that I find the content more engaging and informative.

detailed_results.request: Add RSS feed support so readers can subscribe to new articles
detailed_results.user_story: As an end-user, I need RSS feed support for the website, so that I can subscribe to new articles and receive updates automatically without visiting the site frequently.

detailed_results.request: Reduce blog page load time to under 2 seconds
detailed_results.user_story: As a website user, I need the blog page to load in under 2 seconds, so that I have a seamless and efficient browsing experience.

detailed_results.request: Integrate Google Analytics to track article views and user engagement
detailed_results.user_story: As a developer, I need to integrate Google Analytics to track article views and user engagement, so that we can gather insights on content performance and improve user experience.

detailed_results.request: Add mutation testing to the test suite to improve test effectiveness
detailed_results.user_story: As a QE lead, I need to incorporate mutation testing into the test suite, so that the effectiveness of our tests is improved by identifying inadequacies in the test cases.

detailed_results.request: Build a plagiarism detection system that checks articles against existing content before publishing
detailed_results.user_story: As a content editor, I need a plagiarism detection system that checks articles against existing content before publishing, so that we can ensure originality and avoid legal issues.

detailed_results.request: Handle graceful degradation when external services (OpenAI, GitHub) are unavailable
detailed_results.user_story: As a system, I need to handle graceful degradation when external services are unavailable, so that the application can continue to provide value to the users without significant disruption.
